				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-t%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-t%E1%BB%A9-m%E1%BA%B7c-ho%E1%BA%A1-long/poem-cpBgfNB6Q1Q5P1YnSkT02A">Đại tạ ngự tứ mặc hoạ long - 代謝御賜墨畫龍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/author-KitWPFSrhqgQGR4JMcSBew">Nguyễn Ức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-th%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o/poem-ZqLXl5fWR7oVFvvQDGOmjQ">Đạo thất đạo - 盜失盜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/%C4%90i%E1%BB%81n-vi%C3%AAn-l%E1%BA%A1c-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-Km9CR2lq3Sptq9PpbQK9hw">Điền viên lạc kỳ 2 - 田園樂其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%C3%A3-T%E1%BB%95-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/Gi%C3%A1-ph%C3%A1t-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Kinh/poem-ignOOt9-hec0jLvzdg9fXQ">Giá phát Thượng Kinh - 駕發上京</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%C3%A3-T%E1%BB%95-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-yyTn7TVPngeU_4xv-pnSXQ">Mã Tổ Thường</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/M%E1%BB%99c-Lan-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-6sfuvKunKe6MYqxIDetwJA">Mộc Lan từ - 木蘭詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Th%C3%A1i-H%C3%A0ng-l%E1%BB%99/poem-7VaC8RXuJ80PZ9SXfvj-vg">Thái Hàng lộ - 太行路</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Huy-T%E1%BA%A5n/Tri%E1%BB%81u-h%E1%BB%93i-h%E1%BB%89-ph%C3%BA/poem-4mIFtbpooOMqE0Nxb_Ltxw">Triều hồi hỉ phú - 朝回喜賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Huy-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-Ptt2M8z98OAIiQfyBrIxHw">Vũ Huy Tấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A2u-X%E1%BB%A9-C%C6%A1/V%E1%BB%8Dng-B%E1%BB%93ng-Lai-Du-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-Uoy2mSjnk7btxI4Fq9Zp3A">Vọng Bồng Lai - Du hứng - 望蓬萊—遊興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A2u-X%E1%BB%A9-C%C6%A1/author-Xdrx9PY_HQVilIv5qP5QxQ">Khâu Xứ Cơ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-t%C3%A1i-t%C3%A1c/poem-kse8kfaCIbQYbXultvHmSA">Xuất tái tác - 出塞作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Th%C3%ADch/Y%C3%AAn-ca-h%C3%A0nh/poem-OfaWWw-KGC1o9UcQz3Jy1g">Yên ca hành - 燕歌行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Th%C3%ADch/author-daTT9TQ-QJ39piO86WPo5Q">Cao Thích</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
